content:
The last couple of days #wfh I don’t hear:
*The hum of planes overhead our house 
**The buzz of the highway close by
***The clanking of construction cranes
I hear:
*Windchimes
* Birds
* Squirrels...nature...

Earth must be recovering!!!
renderedContent:
The last couple of days #wfh I don’t hear:
*The hum of planes overhead our house 
**The buzz of the highway close by
***The clanking of construction cranes
I hear:
*Windchimes
* Birds
* Squirrels...nature...

Earth must be recovering!!!

content:
Day 33 of #WFH. I’ve left the flat twice in those 33 days. I miss everything about the normal way of life, even the stuff that pisses me off.

I miss family, friends and colleagues. I miss the gigs. I miss eating out. I miss my bike ride to work.

Can we have it all back please.
